songs.title: The Reaper
songs.lyrics:
I've gone too far
All feelings have died
Hopeless and drugged
Slip into the void

No reason to live
No reason to die
No reason to live
The reaper is laughing

I've gone too far
All feelings have died
Hopeless and drugged
Slip into the void

Slip into the void
Slip into the void
Slip into the void
